# FreePDK45/Nangate KLayout LEF/DEF layer map
#
# Format understood by KLayout LEF/DEF reader:
#   <layer_name> <purpose> <gds_layer> <gds_datatype>
#
# Keep this map purpose-aware so DEF routes/pins/obs and LEF-generated VIA
# geometry are materialized during KLayout stream-out.

# Die outline / boundary
OUTLINE      DIEAREA   100 0

# Routing metals
metal1       DRAWING    34 0
metal1       NET        34 0
metal1       SPNET      34 0
metal1       PIN        34 0
metal1       LABEL      34 0
metal1       LEFPIN     34 0
